            "sections": [
                {
                    "name": "Hatred of Dragons",
                    "type": "sidebar",
                    "text": "Some scholars have speculated that behirs are somehow related to <a aonid=\"34\" game-obj=\"MonsterFamilies\">blue dragons</a>, citing their reptilian features, lightning breath, and ability to speak the <a aonid=\"2\" game-obj=\"Languages\">Draconic</a> language, but such scholars would do well to keep such opinions from behirs they encounter in the field. Nothing infuriates a behir faster than likening it to a dragon!",
